	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f101774250550870><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=7&mid=101774250550870>RE: looking into the class</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=7&mid=101774250550870#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=89825><span id=Sage>Colphax Quick Hands</span></a>, <span id=Sage>Sage</span><br><span id=notbold>105 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Tue, Apr 2nd 5:19 AM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.66]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>It's definately a change of pace from my Ranger Main, but I like it...although the fact that I usually play my Cleric with Warrior and Chanter friends probably has something to do with it.&nbsp;&nbsp;Having friends who you know and trust and know what they are doing is invaluable.<br><br>I've found that if I seem to have extra manna to spare, cast a DD or stun or to the mob's way helps.  I like the idea of being the one who gets the heal off in time to prevent the MA from pushing up daisies.  It's a challenge to keep everyone in fighting trim while you keep the manna usage down.  My current project is to figure out when the best time to cast Celestial Remedy is.  It's nice to cast a spell that won't generate a lot of aggro, heals quite a bit (for it's level), but is a MANNA HOG!!!<br><br>As an aside, my Chanter friend recently tried to get into a Highkeep Stairs Goblin group...and was told by the group leader that an Enchanter was not wanted!!!!! LOL, oh, the humanity!!!!!  Can you see the same guy in a chain-pulling group in a few levels? Poor guy, he's already ticked off one of the best chanters I know, too... <br><br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Apr  2 05:19:20 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Colphax<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=187084" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=187084</a><br>Baradur 30 Human Cleric<br>Malden 16 Dwarven Warrior</td></tr>
